AT.name: Zombie Panic in Wonderland DX
AT.description: The Deluxe Version for Nintendo 3DS™ of the successful Zombie Panic in Wonderland! Don’t miss it! The game is completely renewed for this version! - Amazing graphics! - Extra stages and extended story! - Exclusive enemies! - You can use 2 different control systems which are perfectly adapted for the console! - Maximized playability Let’s set out on a grand adventure to save the Wonderland from the zombies destroying all in your way!
